appDetails.recentChangesHtml: General fixes in check out page

creator: Exceed
descriptionHtml:
Get what you need delivered at your door easily with convenient.
After downloading the App, you can browser and explore our subscribed restaurants and shops located around you. You can view all available and important details which helps you to decide what you like.
All subscribed restaurants and shops are listed in a list where you can see, check their menu items, read description, see images, and many other information, all that put at your finger to enjoy easy ordering process.
You can choose to collect the order by yourself saving you the time and effort of placing the order over the phone, and time in the restaurants waiting for the order to be prepared. in addition, you can also choose for your order to be delivered to your door.
descriptionShort: Browse many subscribed restaurants to get your order delivered at your door.
